1st, draw a shape of Christmas tree on the paper like picture shows;
2nd, cut a piece of long enough aluminum wire and twist it according to the shape of the Christmas tree as picture shows;
3rd, slide a 8mm glass pearl bead to the wire and cut the end of it.

1st, wrap the the last part of the wire to form a circle as picture shows;
2nd, attach a earring hook to the top of the wire wrapped patterns;
3rd, repeat the same ways to complete the other one of these wire wrapped earrings.

1st, slide an 8mm green pearl bead, two 3mm white pearl beads, two 6x3mm pearl beads, a 6mm red pearl bead onto a safety pin in order;
2nd, close the safety pin and make another seven same patterns;
3rd, cut off a piece of fishing wire and slide them onto the wire, then tighten the wire and make them into the below pattern;
4th, make a tie and cut off the extra part.

1st, cut off another piece of fishing wire and slide 2mm seed beads, 3mm white pearl beads, 6mm white pearl beads, 4mm red pearl beads onto the wire;
2nd, thread the wire through the next safety pin and slide the same beads onto the wire in each two space;
3rd, cross the wires through the last safety pin and slide ten 2mm seed beads and a 4mm red pearl bead onto the wire.

1st, thread the wire through the next safety pin and continue to slide seed beads and red pearl beads;
2nd, keep continuing add beads until the whole pattern has been finished;
3rd, slide a 4mm green pearl bead onto a piece of wire and fix it onto the center part of the pattern;
4th, tighten the wire and cut off the extra part, then thread a piece of tiger tail through a 4mm red pearl bead (as shown in the picture).

1st, prepare a long piece of red nylon thread, slide a silver crimp bead, a bead tip, a 2mm white seed bead, two 2mm red seed beads, a 2mm golden seed bead, two 2mm red seed beads, two 2mm white seed beads, a 4mm red seed bead, a red glass bead, a 4mm red seed bead, and twelve 2mm golden seed beads onto the thread;
2nd, cross the thread through the 4mm red seed bead, red glass bead, and 4mm red seed bead pattern, just like the following picture shows;
3rd, tighten the thread to finish the first basic flower layer;
4th, keep adding beads in the same way.

1st, repeat step 1 to finish all 16 flower layers;
2nd, slide two 2mm white seed beads, two 2mm red seed beads, one 2mm golden seed bead, two 2mm red seed beads, one 2mm white seed bead, a sliver bead tip, and a silver crimp bead onto the thread;
3rd, cross the thread back through the previous beads like picture shows.

1st, add two 2mm white seed beads, three 2mm red seed beads, one 2mm golden seed bead, one 4mm red seed bead, one 2mm golden seed bead, three 2mm red seed beads, and two 2mm white seed beads onto the thread and cross the thread through the third to fifth golden seed bead of the first flower layer;
2nd, tighten the thread to make a seed bead flower petal;
3rd, add two 2mm white seed beads, three 2mm red seed beads, one 2mm golden seed bead, one 4mm red seed bead, one 2mm golden seed bead, and three 2mm red seed beads onto the thread, and cross the thread through two 2mm white seed beads of the first petal and a 2mm golden seed bead of the first flower layer;
4th, tighten the thread to make the second seed bead petal.

1st, repeat step 3 to finish all the five seed bead flower petals;
2nd, once all five petals are finished, cross the thread back through the nearby seed beads like picture shows;
3rd, add two 2mm white seed beads, three 2mm red seed beads, one 2mm golden seed bead, and a 4mm red seed bead onto the thread, and cross the thread through the golden seed bead on the last petal.

1st, tighten the thread to connect the first and second pattern;
2nd, add three 2mm red seed beads and two 2mm white seed beads onto the thread and cross them to the nearby golden seed beads like picture show;
3rd, tighten the thread to finish the first petal of the second flower;
4th, make the other four petals of the second flower in the same way.

1st, repeat step 3 to step 5 to finish all the second layer of the 16 flower patterns;
2nd, cross the thread back through the last few seed beads like picture show;
3rd, cross the thread through the lass petal like picture shows, and then add five 2mm golden seed beads onto the thread.

1st, tighten the thread to make a tiny golden seed bead petal;
2nd, add two 2mm golden seed beads to connect the nearby two petals together;
3rd, add five 2mm golden seed beads onto the thread, cross the thread golden seed beads and 4mm red glass bead on the second petal, then tighten the thread to make the second tiny golden seed bead petal.

1st, repeat step 7 to finish all the third layer of the first flower pattern;
2nd, cross the thread through the connecting beads to the second flower pattern;
3rd, finish all the third layers of the flower patterns in the same way.

- a white thick board (A5 size – 21 cm x 14.8 cm);
- hot melt glue sticks: green and transparent ;
- pearl white for the background;
- different colors for the background;
- one green mosaic square piece;
- contour liner paste and glitter;
- modelling paste for the frame;
- the hot tool gun;
- liquid silicone for bonding the mosaic.

- I made the sketch with a red pen;
- I painted the background with the white pearl;
The effect was slightly satiny.

1st, cut a piece of white lace and 2 pieces of blue ribbon according to your wrist;
2nd, cross the ribbons along the lace from one end to the other end as pictured;
3rd, glue a blue dome cabochon to a flower pendant and glue the pendant to middle of the lace pattern.

1st, glue 5 blue drop acrylic rhinestone montee beads to the lace pattern around the flower pendant;
2nd, cut a piece of yellow felt according to length of the lace pattern;
3rd, glue the felt on back of the lace pattern and fold lace to its back and glue them together as pictured.

1st, cut about 400cm 0.2mm white fishing wire and add 4 10mm white round pearl beads to the middle of it (as shown in the picture);
2nd, tighten some knots with the two wires and cut off one wire (as shown in the picture);
3rd, add a 4mm white round pearl bead. Then, cross the wire through the adjacent 10mm white round pearl bead (as shown in the picture);
4th, refer to the above step to add 3 more 4mm white round pearl beads and cross the wire through the 10mm white round pearl beads (as shown in the picture).

1st, add 4 3mm white pearl beads, an 8x6mm white abacus glass bead and 4 3mm white pearl beads to the wire (as shown in the picture);
2nd, cross the wire through the 4mm white pearl bead, the 10mm white pearl bead and the 4mm white pearl bead (as shown in the picture);
3rd, add 4 3mm white pearl beads (as shown in the picture);
4th, cross the wire through the 8x6mm white abacus glass bead (as shown in the picture);
5th, add 4 3mm white pearl beads and cross the wire through the white pearl beads (as shown in the picture).

1st, add 6 3mm white pearl beads (as shown in the picture);
2nd, cross the wire through the 4mm white pearl bead. Then, add 3 3mm white pearl beads, a 3.2mm golden round bead and 3 3mm white pearl beads (as shown in the picture);
3rd, cross the wire through the white pearl beads. Then, add 3 3mm white pearl beads, a 3.2mm golden round bead and 3 3mm white pearl beads and cross the wire through the adjacent 4mm white pearl bead (as shown in the picture);
4th, cross the wire through the adjacent 3mm white pearl bead. Then, add 2 4mm white round seed beads (as shown in the picture)；
5th, cross the needle through the 3mm white pearl bead and the 2 4mm white round seed beads (as shown in the picture).

1st, add a 4mm white round seed bead and cross the wire through the 3mm white pearl bead and seed bead. Repeat this step 5 times (as shown in the picture)；
2nd, add a 3mm white pearl bead and cross the wire through the seed beads (as shown in the picture);
3rd, refer to the above step to add more 3mm white pearl beads. refer to the above steps to make a similar part on the other end (as shown in the picture);
4th, add 3 3.2mm golden round beads (as shown in the picture);
5th, cross the wire through the pearl bead and the golden round beads (as shown in the picture);
6th, add 8 8mm white round pearl beads and 7 golden round beads (as shown in the picture);

1st, cut a piece of adhesive tapes, then put it in the flower pendant and make it tally with the inside shape of the pendant as picture shows;
2nd, cut the spare parts around the pendant like picture shows;
3rd, use glue to tightly connect the flower pendant with the flat round glass cabochon.

1st, use the dark blue nail polish to paint the full oval shape of the Tibetan style pendant like picture shows;
2nd, put some mini glass beads into the pendant until it is fully filled like picture shows;
3rd, use some glue to tightly connect the big Tibetan pendant with the clear glass cabochon.

1st, attach 3 brass jump rings to the 3 Tibetan necklace pendants respectively like picture shows;
2nd, add 3 piece of antique bronze cross chains to the 3 pendants respectively;
3rd, attach 2 brass jump rings to the two ends of the chain and connect the two ends with a brass clasp;
4th, repeat the same steps to finish the other two chain necklaces as picture shows.

1st, cut about 300cm 0.2mm white fishing wire. Then, thread a spring ring necklace end clasp to the middle of the wire. Add 5 2mm white round seed beads to the left wire and 4 2mm white round seed beads to the right wire (as shown in the picture);
2nd, make some knots with the two wires and cut off the upper wire (as shown in the picture);
3rd, add a 2mm white round seed bead and a 6mm clear bicone glass bead. Repeat this step twice (as shown in the picture);
4th, cross the wire through the clear glass beads and seed beads (as shown in the picture);
5th, add 2 2mm white round seed beads and a 6mm clear bicone glass bead. Repeat this step once. Then, add a 2mm white round seed bead (as shown in the picture);
6th, cross the wire through the second seed bead (count from bottom to top). Then, add a 2mm white round seed bead and a 6mm clear bicone glass bead (as shown in the picture).

1st, add 3 white seed beads, a 6mm clear bicone glass bead and 2 white seed beads in sequence (as shown in the picture);
2nd, cross the wire through the seed bead. Then, add a white seed bead, a 6mm clear bicone glass bead, 3 white seed beads, a 6mm red bicone glass bead and a white seed bead in sequence(as shown in the picture);
3rd, cross the wire through the second seed bead (as shown in the picture);
4th, add a white seed bead, a red glass bead, 2 white seed beads, a red glass bead and a white seed bead in sequence (as shown in the picture);
5th, cross the wire through the second seed bead (count from bottom to top). Then, add a white seed bead, a red glass bead, 3 white seed beads, a red glass bead and a white seed bead in sequence (as shown in the picture);
6th, cross the wire through the second seed bead (as shown in the picture).

1st, refer to the 2nd step to the 3rd step in Step 2 to make another bead pattern (as shown in the picture);
2nd, refer to the 4th step to the 6th step in Step 2 to make another red glass bead pattern (as shown in the picture);
3rd, refer to the above steps to make more such bead patterns (as shown in the picture);

1st, tailor a piece of butterfly shape with white felt;
2nd, cut a piece of copper wire and slide a 3mm yellow pearl bead to middle of it;
3rd, add a brown 12x8mm drop glass bead to both ends of the wire and slide 6m yellow pearl beads, a clear abacus glass bead, a pink drop glass bead and a yellow pearl bead to each wire respectively on sequence, then cross both wires back through the beads to fix them;
4th, glue a white drop acrylic rhinestone bead and a drop turquoise bead to both wings of the felt butterfly as pictured;
5th, glue the ready bead pattern onto middle of the butterfly as tentacle with hot glue gun.

1st, sew enough blue seed beads around the wing of the butterfly with needle and white sewing thread;
2nd, continue to sew enough blue seed beads around other 3 wings of the butterfly as pictured;
3rd, slide enough clear abacus glass beads and yellow pearl beads alternatively to the white sewing thread and sew them around the blue seed beads of the wings as pictured;
4th, sew 2 brown faceted round glass beads and a yellow pearl bead in sequence to middle of the butterfly as body pattern.

1st, sew enough blue seed beads to middle of the butterfly around the brown glass beads;
2nd, sew a pink faceted bicone glass bead to both lower wings of the butterfly and sew a pink faceted bicone glass bead beside the wings as pictured;
3rd, sew 3 clear abacus glass beads to edge of both upper wings respectively;
4th, add a flower chandelier component finding to the left lower wing and the right upper wing with glue gun.

1st, cut about 180cm 0.2mm white fishing wire. Then, thread a platinum spring end clasp to the middle of it. Then, thread 4 2mm white seed beads to the nether wire and 5 2mm white seed beads to the upper wire (as shown in the picture);
2nd, make some knots with the two wires and cut off one wire (as shown in the picture);
3rd, thread 4 2mm white seed beads, a 6mm clear bicone glass bead, a 4mm clear bicone glass bead, a 3mm white round pearl bead, a 4mm clear bicone glass bead, a 6mm clear bicone glass bead and 4 2mm white seed beads (as shown in the picture);4th, cross the wire through the middle 3mm white round pearl bead (as shown in the picture).

1st, thread 7 2mm white seed beads (as shown in the picture);
2nd, cross the wire through the left 6 2mm white seed beads added just now and the middle 3mm white pearl bead in sequence (as shown in the picture);
3rd, add 7 white seed beads to the wire. Then, cross the wire through the 6 2mm white seed beads added just now, the middle 3mm white pearl bead and the white seed bead beside the white pearl bead (as shown in the picture);
4th, add a 4mm clear bicone glass bead and a 6mm clear bicone glass bead to the wire. Then, cross the wire through the top white seed bead as shown in the picture);
5th, add a 4mm clear bicone glass bead, a 3mm white pearl bead and a 4mm clear bicone glass bead. Then, cross the wire through the bottom seed bead as shown in the picture);
6th, add a 6mm clear bicone glass bead and a 4mm clear bicone glass bead in sequence to the wire. Then, cross the wire through the seed beads, white pearl beads and glass bead (as shown in the picture).

1st, refer to the 1st step to the 3rd step in Step 2 to add 7 white seed beads on the two sides of the middle white pearl bead respectively (as shown in the picture);
2nd, refer to the above steps to make more such bead patterns (as shown in the picture);
3rd, add about 9 white seed beads. Then, add a silver jump ring (as shown in the picture);
4th, make a hoop with the 9 white seed beads by crossing the wire through the middle white pearl bead and the white seed beads(as shown in the picture).

1st, cut about 80cm 0.2mm white fishing wire. Then, thread 4 6mm white round pearl beads to it (as shown in the picture);
2nd, make some knots with the left wire and the right wire. Then, cross the left wire through adjacent white pearl bead and the cut off the excess wire (as shown in the picture);
3rd, thread 3 6mm white round pearl beads;
4th, combine the three white pearl beads together by crossing the wire through the left bottom white pearl bead of the four bead pattern, then crossing the wire through the two white pearl beads(as shown in the picture);
5th, refer to the Step 3 and Step 4 to make another such bead pattern. Then, add a 6mm white round pearl bead and cross the wire through the leftmost white pearl bead. Then, add a 6mm white round pearl bead and cross the wire through the rightmost white pearl bead (as shown in the picture);
6th, tighten the wire.

1st, add a 6mm white round pearl bead and cross the wire through the adjacent white pearl beads. Refer to this step to add 3 more 6mm white round pearl beads (as shown in the picture);
2nd, add a pink abacus glass beads and cross the wire through the white pearl beads (as shown in the picture);
3rd, refer to the above step to add 3 more pink abacus glass beads (as shown in the picture);
4th, refer to the above steps to make another white pearl beads and pink glass beads pattern and a white pearl beads and blue glass beads pattern (as shown in the picture);
5th, thread a golden eyepin to the three bead patterns respectively. Then, make a hoop on the other end of the three eyepins one by one(as shown in the picture).

1st, combine 3 8x6mm dark salmon abacus glass beads, a pink abacus glass bead, 2 blue abacus glass beads, 4 6mm white pearl beads and 5 clear abacus glass beads with golden headpins (as shown in the picture);
2nd, cut a piece of 4x3mm golden chain. Then, add a pink glass bead, a white pearl bead, a blue glass bead and a clear glass bead to the chain(as shown in the picture);
3rd, cut 4 pieces of 4x3mm golden chains. Then, add the beads to the chains (as shown in the picture);
4th, combine the five chains together through a golden jump ring. Then, add a silver circular component to the top through jump rings (as shown in the picture);
5th, use glue gun to attach a white peony resin flower bead, 2 purple rose flower resin beads and a yellow rose flower resin bead onto the silver circular component (as shown in the picture);
6th, use glue gun to attach a 10mm white round pearl bead, a purple rose flower resin bead, 2 6mm white round pearl beads and a pink abacus glass bead onto the silver circular component (as shown in the picture).

1st, use glue gun to attach a red peony resin flower bead and a pink peony resin flower bead onto a golden square component respectively (as shown in the picture);
2nd, add the white pearl bead ball pattern with blue glass beads (as shown in the picture);
3rd, cut two equal pieces of golden twisted chain and combine them with the white pearl bead ball pattern with blue glass beads. Then, add the red peony resin flower bead pattern and the pink peony resin flower bead (as shown in the picture);
4th, cut two equal pieces of golden twisted chain. Then, combine them with the two peony resin flower bead patterns respectively. Then, add the two white pearl bead ball pattern with pink glass beads to the two sides respectively. Cut two equal pieces of golden twisted chain and combine them with the two white pearl bead ball patterns (as shown in the picture);
5th, add a 10mm white pearl bead to the left chain and a golden spring clasp to the right chain (as shown in the picture);

